---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Company Profile | Black62 Commodities"
  description="Black62 Commodities full company profile — heritage, services, commodities, 62-ton heavy-haul fleet and registration details."
  canonical="https://www.black62.co.za/company-profile/"
  headerScrolled
>
  <article class="subpage">
    <div class="container content">
      <p class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:1rem">Company Profile</p>
      <h1 class="silver">Black62 Commodities (Pty) Ltd</h1>
      <p class="meta">Trading and bulk logistics — coal, chrome and animal feed.</p>

      <div class="actions">
        <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="window.print()">Download PDF</button>
        <button class="btn btn-outline" onclick="window.print()">Print</button>
      </div>

      <section>
        <h2>About the Company</h2>
        <p>Black62 Commodities is the new identity of Tsogang Brands (Pty) Ltd, registered in 2015 under registration number 2015/115352/07. The rebrand reflects a sharpened focus on the physical trading of coal, chrome and animal feed, supported by a specialised 62-ton abnormal heavy-haul road freight fleet across South Africa and the wider SADC region.</p>
        <p>Our management team brings together more than two decades of combined experience across mining, energy, agriculture and freight. We are headquartered in Roodepoort, Gauteng.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Vision</h2>
        <p>To become Africa's most dependable trading and logistics partner for industrial and agricultural commodities — connecting reputable producers to domestic and global buyers with discipline, transparency and scale.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Mission</h2>
        <p>We move the right material to the right buyer at the right time — with full compliance, fair pricing and reliable execution.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Core Commodities</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Coal</strong> — Thermal and metallurgical grade coal for power, industry and export.</li>
          <li><strong>Chrome</strong> — Chrome ore and concentrate to local smelters and export markets.</li>
          <li><strong>Animal Feed</strong> — Bulk feed for livestock, poultry, dairy and feedlot operations.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Logistics Capabilities</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>62-ton abnormal heavy-haul road freight, with permit and escort coordination</li>
          <li>Cross-border SADC movements with full documentation</li>
          <li>Fleet management, dispatch and turnaround scheduling</li>
          <li>Weighbridge tickets, seals and chain-of-custody on every load</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Compliance &amp; Registration</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Registered Entity: Tsogang Brands (Pty) Ltd t/a Black62 Commodities</li>
          <li>Registration Number: 2015/115352/07</li>
          <li>VAT Number: 4870279298</li>
          <li>B-BBEE Compliant</li>
          <li>SARS &amp; regulatory aligned</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Head Office</h2>
        <p>22 Bedien Street, Culembeeck AH, Roodepoort, 1724, South Africa</p>
        <p>Email: <a href="mailto:info@black62.co.za">info@black62.co.za</a></p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
